### PASETO Login
POST http://localhost:3001/paseto/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

### Save refresh token and logout
POST http://localhost:3001/paseto/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}
